# Ignore file for the PUBLIC forkable project (used by ./push-public.sh).
#
# Deliberately NARROWER than .claspignore: it pushes only the four app sources
# and never the one-off vocab-maintenance scripts. Those are private tooling and
# must not land in a project strangers are going to copy. Do not add whitelist
# lines here for maintenance scripts — that is what .claspignore is for.
**/**
!appsscript.json
!Code.js
!Index.html
!Seed.js
